  "text": "The Weissenberg-Rabinowitsch correction for the round die (Eq. (3)) considers the fact that the shear rate mentioned in Eq. (2) is only valid for Newtonian fluids and provides the true shear rate at the capillary wall for them [CITATION_1] .",
